# Cron jobs for the container
# Timezone is set by the TZ env var in the Dockerfile
#
# Format: minute hour day-of-month month day-of-week command
#   *  *  *  *  *  command
#   |  |  |  |  |
#   |  |  |  |  +---- day of week  (0-7, Sunday=0 or 7)
#   |  |  |  +------- month        (1-12)
#   |  |  +---------- day of month (1-31)
#   |  +------------- hour         (0-23)
#   +---------------- minute       (0-59)
#
# Examples:
#   Run every minute:
#   * * * * * python /app/job.py >> /var/log/cron.log 2>&1
#
#   Run daily at midnight:
#   0 0 * * * python /app/job.py >> /var/log/cron.log 2>&1
#
#   Run every hour:
#   0 * * * * python /app/job.py >> /var/log/cron.log 2>&1

